description.en:
What is the project about?
The character Reaper was inspired by the famous Grim Reaper crypto meme and the well-known cartoon called Billy and Mandy. Reaper is fed up with all the meme scams/rug pulls/pump&dumps going on and is on a mission to wipe out their liquidity and become the biggest meme so far.

What makes your project unique?
Very unique meme, amazing degen artists, top influencers onboard and well connected/active team.

History of your project.
We have worked on the idea of launching reaper for about 3 months after we saw some Reaper memes online and the idea was originated from that.

What’s next for your project?
We are planning to launch NFTs

What can your token be used for?
It's a meme token for now but soon it will be used for NFTs.
